title: Daddy D - Kokoriko
seo_description: A good blend of folklore, jazz and afro beats , kokoriko is one of it's kind. Soft yet hard with powerful lyrics. Daddy D on this one wishes everybody a happy new year. He is asking you to keep the faith and the flames burning because there is hope.
description:
<!--StartFragment-->

A good blend of folklore, jazz and afro beats , kokoriko is one of it's kind. Soft yet hard with powerful lyrics. Daddy D on this one wishes everybody a happy new year. He is asking you to keep the faith and the flames burning because there is hope.
